        // Implementation
    }
    
    func stopRecording() -> URL? {
        // Implementation
    }
}
```

## üéØ Swift CLI Development Workflow

### Development Philosophy
- **CLI-First**: Use `swift build` and `swift run` for all development
- **Logger-Based Debugging**: Rely on Logger.swift for all debugging needs
- **Text Editor Freedom**: Use any text editor (VS Code, Vim, etc.)
- **Xcode Only When Needed**: Only use Xcode for final packaging and code signing

